@page "/animals/lions"

<main>
    <header class="hero">
        <img src="/images/lion-hero.jpg" alt="Lions in the Wild" class="hero-image" />
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Lions: The King of the Jungle</h1>
            <p>Explore the life of lions, their pride, and the savannah they call home.</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="text-img">
            <div class="content-text">
                <h2>Life in the Pride</h2>
                <p>Lions live in social groups known as prides, which include females, their cubs, and a dominant male. They are renowned for their majestic mane and formidable hunting skills.</p>
            </div>
            <img src="/images/lion-pride.jpg" alt="Lion Pride" />
        </div>

        <div class="video-section">
            <h2>Watch a Lion Hunt</h2>
            <video controls>
                <source src="/videos/lion-hunt.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
        <h2>Ready to See Lions Up Close?</h2>
        <a href="/book-options" class="cta-button">Book Your Visit</a>
    </section>
</main>
